{"tid":486142,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"大家中意狗多啲定貓？","createTime":"2017-12-01T14:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T16:05:40.000Z","uid":80736,"like":27,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f3280d0ce61e437c212ff63f7f4a58f09744d032","tid":486142,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"本人中意狗多，有感情啲貓好仆街，淨係掛住自己玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d53cd70b0d510b2c6e0606540cd19e83d7fffca","tid":486142,"uid":11774,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:24:42.000Z","msg":"狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓係靚 但做唔到狗嗰種互動<br />\n貓係佢想玩先會撩你玩<br />\n但狗係真心眼中只有你嗰種"},{"pid":"c50c4c1d249cb4728ca3a560076e7cda96c84635","tid":486142,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓係靚 但做唔到狗嗰種互動<br />\n貓係佢想玩先會撩你玩<br />\n但狗係真心眼中只有你嗰種</blockquote><br />\n終於有同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e01fac298c320a1b9252102026791bad22982c1","tid":486142,"uid":11774,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓係靚 但做唔到狗嗰種互動<br />\n貓係佢想玩先會撩你玩<br />\n但狗係真心眼中只有你嗰種</blockquote><br />\n終於有同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好鍾意佢跟住自己嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊瞓覺嗰陣會痴住你瞓 個頭係都要痴住我個頭 對手仲要攬住我條頸 無論點嬲佢都好 佢會氹返你<br />\n就算用緊電腦上網 佢都係望住你<br />\n但貓 有種做奴隸 服侍佢咁 而無嗰種人與寵物之間嘅羈絆"},{"pid":"ee99d0c90c18be41a23239511fbb4ea9bfd05ff5","tid":486142,"uid":11774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓係靚 但做唔到狗嗰種互動<br />\n貓係佢想玩先會撩你玩<br />\n但狗係真心眼中只有你嗰種</blockquote><br />\n終於有同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好鍾意佢跟住自己嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊瞓覺嗰陣會痴住你瞓 個頭係都要痴住我個頭 對手仲要攬住我條頸 無論點嬲佢都好 佢會氹返你<br />\n就算用緊電腦上網 佢都係望住你<br />\n但貓 有種做奴隸 服侍佢咁 而無嗰種人與寵物之間嘅羈絆</blockquote><br />\n重點係 可以帶埋隻狗去街 係一件好開心嘅事 喺街邊啲小食店 坐埋一齊享受出街樂趣 又可以一齊去海灘喎 貓好少會帶出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3858f6bcd67196a2ec105f2dedef185b8d218b3","tid":486142,"uid":151630,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:06:24.000Z","msg":"我鍾意貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最唔鍾意狗嗰種愚忠"},{"pid":"b296d8446a5e2e7728fe54931225bc123566648c","tid":486142,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我鍾意貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最唔鍾意狗嗰種愚忠</blockquote><br />\n愚忠？"},{"pid":"03a76ad2069d2f6dc9eeb3db2dab51df81e0f3e5","tid":486142,"uid":11774,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:29:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我鍾意貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最唔鍾意狗嗰種愚忠</blockquote><br />\n與其話佢哋愚忠 不如話係好似朋友咁不離不棄啦<br />\n我阿媽扮嘢打我 佢會撲過嚟保護我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而佢喺街見到大狗 就會到我保護返佢"},{"pid":"ca7620a1a0636423c4626cab328167edf15df86b","tid":486142,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"貓狗都係垃圾"},{"pid":"89bc0a812a0b238bbe30046dbb5c49b699d30b56","tid":486142,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:34:59.000Z","msg":"狗"},{"pid":"fe8b51be474f5e952a3ef0b2b5815f0b3c4437bd","tid":486142,"uid":16652,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:53:29.000Z","msg":"貓的身體<br />\n狗的靈魂<b